dc_description_s: AMS 2. Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. 4375. Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. 4410. Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. 4412. Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. 4413. Alternate title: Craiova, Romania. Universal transverse Mercator and Danube zone grids. UTM grid added, gradient tints and isogonic data deleted by AMS, 1947. Relief shown by 50 and 100 meter contour intervals and spot elevations. With Romanian and Bulgarian glossaries. Corrected from intelligence reports up to February 1943. See index. Library holdings for this set are incomplete.
dc_publisher_s: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1948.
